node.text:
ASMR Pokémon Unboxing is back 👀🍃👏🏻

This is a post featured with @cardgameclubit which is one of the best Pokémon online store that I’ve ever seen!🤩👏🏻 I received a full box as you can see of the serie ‘Battle Styles’ and look what I pulled!😭 One of the best card (in my opinion) of this set and I’m very happy that I found it!
Watch the entire video to check out all the cards that I found and be sure to check the page of Card Game Club!💕⠀

node.text:
ASMR Pokémon Unboxing!👀Guys this is the video unboxing in partnership with @fantasiastore.it that sent me these awesome Pokémon’s products that you can see here!!🤧 This is also one of the best Online Shop I ever seen about Pokémon cards and be sure to check it out please!!👀💞 Obviously is not only about Pokémon but you can find also some manga/anime stuff like action figures and funkos!🤩

I wasn’t that lucky like you could see but still had a lot of fun while doing this video!🤣
I hope you enjoyed the video!💕

node.text:
Does my art looks like me?🙈👀🤔
⠀
Ahhhh okay now I’m definitely SHY but I decided to post because why not? 😆👏🏻 Basically I read everyday comments like “omg you really looks like you art!” “This drawing definitely seems you!”😲
I’m always like “no-“ because I can’t actually notice it but does it really like this?🤣👌🏻 My pic with my little cat Danny is my fave between all btw uwu 💕
ANYWAY- I hope you appreciate as the little chibi ver. of me!😆 see ya!💖
.
.
.
